acme.validation.customer.invalid-identifier.message=Invalid identifier. It must follow the pattern ^[A-Z]{2,3}\\d{6}$ and match the customer's initials.
acme.validation.customer.invalid-phone-number.message=Invalid phone number. It must follow the pattern ^\\+?\\d{6,15}$.
acme.validation.customer.invalid-address.message=Invalid address. It must be between 1 and 255 characters.
acme.validation.customer.invalid-city.message=Invalid city. It must be between 1 and 50 characters.
acme.validation.customer.invalid-country.message=Invalid country. It must be between 1 and 50 characters.
acme.validation.customer.invalid-points.message=Invalid points. It must be between 0 and 500,000.